name: Ratu Gede Mecaling
description:
#MaskSeries : Ratu Gede Mecaling

Ratu Gede Mecaling is one of the guards of Bhatara Kala at Pura Dalem Ped Nusa Penida. The task of his role is to send evil spirits or atman to Pura Dalem Kerangkeng. The location of the temple is in Nusa Penida. There is a kerangkeng (prison) cave inside the temple which contains a court table and a statue of Lord Ganesha.
